Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.39,0:00:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还以为朝廷会嫌我官职低微
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.86,0:00:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不肯将徐州敕封于我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.96,0:00:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可现在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不但让我领了徐州牧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.57,0:00:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且还令我奉诏讨贼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.87,0:00:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}征战袁术 攻取南阳郡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}几位兄弟 你们有何建议
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥只管做你的徐州牧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}招兵买马 练兵备战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.88,0:00:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}至于征讨袁术嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那肯定是曹操假借天子之名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}发的矫诏乱命 咱不睬它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.56,0:00:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兄弟此话怕是不妥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:00:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恩诏我们接下了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.67,0:01:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}密旨却斥为矫诏乱命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.17,0:01:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这岂不是说哪个对我们有利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们就接哪个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.78,0:01:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如此的话 非臣子之道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这打就打呗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术也不是什么好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.58,0:01:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们还记得不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这当初征讨董卓的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是这个贼袁术断了咱们的粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老给咱们使坏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.99,0:01:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日能打他个痛快 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以前的事情不提了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日却是因那袁术有不臣之心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天子颁诏 我只能奉旨讨贼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是 大军出征后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.61,0:01:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这徐州城该由谁守备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这可是一桩重任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:01:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可 可别叫我守城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我早就憋坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这征讨袁术 我得做先锋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 我愿留守徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二弟 大军出征
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.97,0:02:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早晚有事我需与你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你必须与我同行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 那就由在下领兵守城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}子龙勇猛过人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是天赐先锋之将
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最好也同我一起出征
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们都出去痛快去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又把我一人丢在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟啊 徐州可是咱们的根基呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}重如性命 你能够把家看好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可是大功一件呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟性情暴躁 遇事易冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能担当此大任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此事从长计议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎 什么话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哥哥也太小看人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要是连个徐州都守不住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哥哥砍了我脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟你果真要守城
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们只管放心去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.07,0:03:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这徐州交给我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我给你定几条规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在我们出征期间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你务必遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥你只管说 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是不要禁我喝酒就成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这第一条便是断不可饮酒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这 这 这不让出去打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经难过死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这不再让喝酒这生不如死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 算了 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行他不行 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哥哥 哥哥 我做得到 做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哥哥你只管说你的规矩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一条 不可饮酒致醉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第二条 不可暴怒任性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三条 不可打骂军士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此三条为军令 你万不可误
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥放心 这许些小事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我保证是严守无误
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等你们凯旋归来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我再开怀痛饮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这 这 这 这 这织席贩履之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}屠猪卖酒之流
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还 还 还 还想谋害我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公骂得可是刘关张三兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正是 你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操给我送来了一封密信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说刘备给朝廷上了一道密奏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诬陷我要称帝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还要发兵攻破我的首府南阳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原本一无名鼠辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却要谎称是皇室后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欺世盗名嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}趁人家陶谦病亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}窃取了偌大一座徐州尚不知足
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还想打我州县
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是可忍敦不可忍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}世风日下 小人得志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备可恨 请主公发兵剿灭他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备固然可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但那曹操就是善良之辈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他说的每一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就句句都是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下以为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此事有几个疑点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备是否真的给朝廷上过密奏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诬陷我家主公有不臣之志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这尚且不清
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其二 就算刘备给朝廷上过密奏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操为何要将此事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}通报给我家主公
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其用意何在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家主公也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其三 曹操和刘备之间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}彼此交恶 要害在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生 你的意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要害是徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备区区之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}得一偌大徐州之城并兼六郡之地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是让天下诸侯都非常眼红的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最为妒恨的就数曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在 刘备和吕布两人联手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:07:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}共守徐州 那是兵强马壮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操他是想攻则不敢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欲弃又不舍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么办 怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他就想挑动主公和刘备打起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}弄得两败俱伤 他好从中谋利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果主公败给刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊不 那是万不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他就势取南阳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果刘备败给主公
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.62,0:07:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他就势取徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生说得极是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}敢问主公 你想不想取徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想啊 我天天在想 我朝思暮想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就趁势取徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下有一计
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可使主公轻取徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生快讲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布虽然晓勇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:08:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他却是三姓家奴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其性多变而又贪婪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他和刘备同处一城 如处水火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果主公贿他以黄金万两
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}锦缎千匹 令他暗中偷袭刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公到时出兵相迎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如此 定能大功告成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.57,0:08:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}事成之后嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公把徐州下的两个郡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}赏给他就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再以后嘛 主公找个机会灭了他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那不是易如反掌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 这是大哥的座位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 主簿何在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎 将军将军来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我大哥把这徐州城交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}临行前给我留下了三条军令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这第一不可饮酒致醉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第二不可暴怒任性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三不可打骂军士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要你把这三条军令写成中堂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悬于这个大梁之上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要天天看 夜夜想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}严守不误
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对了 每一个字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都要给我写得碗口那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要碗口那么大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}废话 俺张飞的字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就得碗口那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:09:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是是 碗口那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这写好之后 悬于梁上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再去传统领以上的将领
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}花亭相见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是 我要训话 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你再去给我准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}俺张飞酿的美酒五十坛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 啊 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你刚才讲的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那主公留下的第一条军令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是不许饮酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你废话 我叫你去办 就去办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是是 小的遵命 遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 我担心三弟会醉酒误事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也担心 不过反过来一想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}翼德如果连酒瘾都扛不住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}日后如何成大事 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是让他历练一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}前后不过几十天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.62,0:11:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实我更担心的还不是翼德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而是吕布 我听说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他与陈宫驻守小沛后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天天都在招兵买马
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 吕布是头饿虎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早晚要生事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你应该把他逐出徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我以仁义待他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只盼他不要负我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他要是负你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他负我是他 我不负仁义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术即送我黄金万两 丝绸千匹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又发兵助我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这可是谋取徐州的大好时机呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是徐州城 哪那么容易攻取
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽 张飞 赵云
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们之勇可都不在将军之下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怕什么 我有赤兔马 方天画戟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何恒于天下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们现在最需要的 就是一座城池
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总不能老是寄人篱下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说不定哪一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我跟刘备闹翻了反目成仇怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还不如先下手为强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样 我的意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这件事情 我们还是要慎重一些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不妨我们先答应袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让他把黄金绸缎先送过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}至于攻打徐州城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们可以再找时机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 干
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喝 好样的 喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}该你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀将军 末将不能喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一口下去 肚子就痛如刀绞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真不能喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这个混帐东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这美酒是包治百病
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪有肚子痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特别是我张飞的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那能强身健体 赛过龙肝凤胆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今儿这酒 你非喝不可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要不喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}便是犯了我的军令了 喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大口喝 我喝干喽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这喝猫尿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大口喝 给我喝净了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将万万喝不得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喝了非死不可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你这是犯了我的军令了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要么罚酒十碗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要么打一百军杖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你自个儿选一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张将军 张将军饶了末将吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}求你看在我表哥的份上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}表哥 你表哥是何许人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我表哥就是上将军吕布啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他跟你大哥刘备亲如兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放屁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布岂能与我大哥做兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你小子今儿不仅犯了我的军令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还拿吕布那厮来唬爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我没有 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 今儿我偏偏要打你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打你就是打那贼吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 将军求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军饶命啊 饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 将军饶命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}男子汉大丈夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}岂能讨救求饶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你应该说 打得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不然我打死你这个贼吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打得好 打得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这就对了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说 你爷爷在打谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军在打罪将曹豹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.61,0:15:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放屁 爷在打贼吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说啊 在打贼吕布 说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}错了 不是吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是贼吕布 贼吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爷在打贼吕布 贼吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爷打得好不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:15:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上将军 徐州城守曹豹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}带伤来投
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹豹 他是我表弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快 快请进来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}表哥 你要为我报仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兄弟 出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那匹夫张飞 借酒发威
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把我打得死去活来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我求他说看我表哥的面子上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}饶我一命 他问我表哥是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说是上将军吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.61,0:16:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}匹夫顿时大怒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}骂表哥你是贱贼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是三姓家奴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还说打我便是打贼吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}直把我打得死去活来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这张飞欺人太甚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:17:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他已经污辱过我好几回了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这次 我绝不饶他 来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快备马 取我方天画戟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}且慢 奉先 先不要着急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹豹 来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}慢慢说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张飞为什么要打你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是你违反了什么军令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张飞非要逼我喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将平生忌酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不敢喝 他便打我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我没有听明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张飞为什么要逼你喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为刘备给张飞下了三道军令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}头一条便是不能饮酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备给张飞下了禁酒令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为刘备率军去征讨袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}城里就剩下张飞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备怕张飞饮酒误事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以才给他下了禁酒令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备率军出征了 此事当真
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}千真万确 昨天出发的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽 赵云同行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽和赵云一同前往
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那为什么徐州城上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关 赵二将的将旗还在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是虚张声势
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实 现在城里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有五 六千老弱守军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}外带一个匹夫张飞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先啊 时机到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上天赐徐州城予你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如若我们不取
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那真是有负苍天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 我亲自领军 直取徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 徐州城坚固无比
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果没有内应 断难攻取
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.51,0:18:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹豹 你愿不愿意立一大功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕将军定会上奏朝廷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜你为中郎将 赐爵封侯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 你作为内应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}马上赶回徐州城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今夜四更 看到火起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打开南城门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.93,0:19:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}的确是虚张声势啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州城已经近乎空城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}发令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}冲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 将军 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你快醒醒 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 将军 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}敌军进城了 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将酒来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 我没醉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布偷袭徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.13,0:20:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹豹 曹豹打开南门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迎吕布进城了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹豹打开南门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迎吕布进城了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布进城了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 将军 这会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布已经把城中各处要寨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}全都给占领了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}传令迎敌 取我兵器来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三将军 三将军 你不能去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.53,0:21:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贼吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贼吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三将军 你不能去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去你的 滚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贼吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}匹夫 快快受死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好你个贼崽子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟敢出卖城池
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你个贼崽子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}死了 走 走 走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.23,0:21:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三将军 咱们快撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.33,0:21:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三将军 快上马吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不走 叫贼吕布过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要跟他大战三百回合
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.34,0:21:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三将军 我们势单力薄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布已经率大军掩杀过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们再不走的话 就来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三将军 还是快点撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不走 贼吕布 贼吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军师 军师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.23,0:22:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军师 我们的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.53,0:22:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}搜到刘备的住宅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他的妻妾在 如何处置
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听令 你等一定要严加看护
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}任何人不得进入
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.15,0:22:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所有供给 一概不得短缺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.45,0:22:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}违者立斩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上将军 东囤粮仓的粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}颗粒不少
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.25,0:22:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备的两万余担军粮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.65,0:22:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}全都归我们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.15,0:23:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.16,0:23:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上将军 北大营不战自降
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}获得战马五百余匹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.03,0:23:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.93,0:23:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上将军 陶谦的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.33,0:23:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也率旧部归降了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.63,0:23:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一不可饮酒致醉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.44,0:23:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二不可暴怒任性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三不可打骂军士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 这个翼德真是可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.95,0:23:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可爱之极啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一碗酒就把三条军令全都违反了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.25,0:23:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还外搭了一座徐州城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.35,0:23:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生 徐州已经完全落入我们手里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各处守军都降了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.93,0:23:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}祝贺将军
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.13,0:23:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过有件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.33,0:23:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可能已经忘记了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.14,0:23:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.54,0:23:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在可以立即通知袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.94,0:23:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}按照先前的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.64,0:23:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们已经取下徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.38,0:23:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他应该给我们送来万两黄金
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.68,0:24:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}千匹绸缎才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.65,0:24:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对 我们可是双喜临门
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.95,0:24:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一箭双雕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.93,0:24:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟不要再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.44,0:24:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州原本就不是我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.94,0:24:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}得何足喜 失何足忧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.28,0:24:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天意 一切皆是天意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.88,0:24:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟 嫂嫂何在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.45,0:24:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都陷在城里了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.63,0:24:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当初你是怎么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.73,0:24:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哥哥又是怎么盼咐你的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.13,0:24:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在丢了城池不说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.93,0:24:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二位嫂嫂也落入了贼兵之手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.34,0:25:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有何面目前来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.88,0:25:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不活了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.48,0:25:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.28,0:25:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不活了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.38,0:25:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.63,0:25:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.83,0:25:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.73,0:25:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}江山已倾覆 谁家不遭殃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.44,0:25:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们三人桃园结义时
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.24,0:25:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}立下过誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.34,0:25:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不求同年同月同日生
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.78,0:25:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但求同年同月同日死
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.18,0:25:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你如果再有此等愚举
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.58,0:25:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为兄绝不独生
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.55,0:25:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.54,0:26:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 哨骑来报
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.64,0:26:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术派上将纪灵
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.14,0:26:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}率十五万大军前来征讨
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.24,0:26:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}距此不到十里了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.78,0:26:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}前有袁术大军 后有叛将吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.45,0:26:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无处容身 进退两难
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.76,0:26:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道上天真的要绝我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.33,0:26:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 我率军迎战纪灵
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.13,0:26:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你固然勇猛无敌
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.84,0:26:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是徐州失陷的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.94,0:26:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经在军中弥漫
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.94,0:26:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兵无斗志 不可再战了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.48,0:26:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那主公准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.88,0:26:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.46,0:26:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州已落入了吕布手里
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.66,0:26:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥你还要得回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.63,0:27:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我没打算要回徐州 也不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.73,0:27:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.53,0:27:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我没有任何对不住吕布的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.73,0:27:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相反
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.93,0:27:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布倒有对不住我的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.84,0:27:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}料想他不会取我首级吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.24,0:27:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们回到徐州 可与吕布商量
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.58,0:27:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州就归他了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.38,0:27:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们暂借小沛落足
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.58,0:27:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那小沛先前是陶谦借予我的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.28,0:27:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}后来我送给了他吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.19,0:27:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们现在重返小沛
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.79,0:27:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布为主驻徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.99,0:27:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们为从驻小沛
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.32,0:27:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}两城互成犄角之势
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.23,0:27:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}共拒曹操和袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.63,0:27:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想来 吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.73,0:27:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不至于过于吝啬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.24,0:27:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 你就是心太善啦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.48,0:27:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 袁术赖帐了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.58,0:27:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.08,0:27:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他在复信上说
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.48,0:27:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们虽然攻下了徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.89,0:28:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却没有取下刘备的首级
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.19,0:28:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以不能给我们黄金绸缎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.03,0:28:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术小人 自己言而无信
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.03,0:28:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却怪我们失约
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.93,0:28:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}争天下之时 生死无度
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.54,0:28:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还谈何信义 依我看
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.44,0:28:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即使你把刘备的脑袋砍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.68,0:28:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给他送去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.48,0:28:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他也未必会送来黄金绸缎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.98,0:28:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他真正贪图的是这座徐州城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.09,0:28:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报 禀上将军
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.69,0:28:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备领兵拜关
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.53,0:28:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来了多少兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.13,0:28:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有刘关张三骑
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.24,0:28:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好大的胆子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.54,0:28:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来 他们不是来攻城
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.74,0:28:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是有求于将军
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.89,0:29:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我如此待他 他还敢来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.29,0:29:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备到底是个君子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.16,0:29:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我亲自出城相见
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.43,0:29:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.43,0:29:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先哪 我有话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.28,0:30:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德 别来无恙
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.99,0:30:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来来来 赶快进去 来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.44,0:30:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德啊 我不是要夺你的城池
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.24,0:30:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是因为张飞兄弟酒醉杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.68,0:30:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}导致军心混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.68,0:30:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我怕他误了守城大事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.08,0:30:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以才引兵来这儿守几天徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.09,0:30:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然玄德回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.36,0:30:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自然应该物归原主
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.46,0:30:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请玄德收下徐州关防
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.07,0:31:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕将军 你我初次在此相见时
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.94,0:31:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下就想将徐州让给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.48,0:31:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在事实证明在下确实无才无德
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.48,0:31:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不配拥有徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.68,0:31:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日之变 可以说是天意
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.88,0:31:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是上天将徐州授予你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.79,0:31:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请将军万勿生疑
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.89,0:31:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是请玄德收下关防吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.56,0:31:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不敢 不敢 天授徐州与你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.46,0:31:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请将军不要再生疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.47,0:31:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然如此 我就恭敬不如从命了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.94,0:31:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}权且替玄德把守徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.74,0:31:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德你自此何去何从呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.58,0:31:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下 确实是无处可去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.79,0:31:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如吕将军允许的话
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.89,0:31:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想暂驻于小沛
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.69,0:32:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样也可与徐州互为犄角之势
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.46,0:32:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}共同抵杭曹操袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.47,0:32:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 玄德兄 那怎么可以呀
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.97,0:32:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样太委屈你了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.34,0:32:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如蒙允许 刘备感恩不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.38,0:32:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德啊 小沛就归你了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.59,0:32:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是你当初那句话
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.69,0:32:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所有粮饷 由我提供
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.96,0:32:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下拜谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.37,0:32:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要咱俩同心 何愁大业不成
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.87,0:32:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们可以徐州为根据
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.44,0:32:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}厉兵秣马 先取袁术次取曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.68,0:32:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再征刘表和公孙瓒 共图天下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.87,0:33:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备是位真君子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.48,0:33:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}受如此大辱 却平静如水
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.38,0:33:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可敬可佩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.08,0:33:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贼吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.39,0:33:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我倒觉得有点儿对不住他了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.19,0:33:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道你不觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.16,0:33:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备可敬可佩之外
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.96,0:33:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更有些可怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.26,0:33:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.17,0:33:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州城乃刘备的根基之地
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.47,0:33:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军趁其不备占为已有
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.17,0:33:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}任何人受到这种奇耻大辱
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.61,0:33:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是万难忍受的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.28,0:34:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是刘备呢 竟然没有一句怨言
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.78,0:34:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}重归小沛 替将军
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.48,0:34:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去看守徐州的北大门去了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.69,0:34:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么样的人才能够做到这种
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.09,0:34:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忍耻含愤 平静如水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.46,0:34:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能够如此这般者
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.76,0:34:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是何等的心胸和志向
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.07,0:34:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这种人不可怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.91,0:34:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}据报 吕布与刘备再度和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.38,0:34:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州小沛二城互为犄角
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.88,0:34:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}联守共拒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.29,0:34:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如此下去 何日可得徐州啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.56,0:34:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果主公想图徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.06,0:34:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就要将刘备和吕布分而治之
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.97,0:34:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先结交吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.57,0:34:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}使他不援刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.07,0:34:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之后攻下小沛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.87,0:34:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再图徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.31,0:35:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这不是把吕布得罪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.81,0:35:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我答应他的金银绸缎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.58,0:35:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我没给他
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.79,0:35:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.79,0:35:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下实在不敢苟同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.79,0:35:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成大事者 不可失信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.06,0:35:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尤其是对小人不可失信
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.36,0:35:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为小人比君子更危险
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.27,0:35:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生说得对呀
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.97,0:35:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可我该怎么办哪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.51,0:35:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.51,0:35:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布现在最想要的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.41,0:35:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他能想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.38,0:35:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}粮饷呗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.59,0:35:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他现在到处招兵买马
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.09,0:35:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到处搜刮粮饷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.76,0:35:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他问主公要多少
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.06,0:35:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这小子狮子大开口
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.96,0:35:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张口就管我要十万粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.07,0:36:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}十万哪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.77,0:36:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给他二十万
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.67,0:36:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二十万
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.67,0:36:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对 二十万
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.71,0:36:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能买到的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.01,0:36:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是便宜货
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.11,0:36:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成大事者 何吝于粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.09,0:36:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 我给他
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.36,0:36:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用力 用力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.76,0:36:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用力 用力 获胜者有赏
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.47,0:36:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.47,0:36:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这孩子 又得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.71,0:36:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用力 用力拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.31,0:36:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 起来 起来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.41,0:36:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先啊 你可真够开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.29,0:36:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我当然开心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.39,0:36:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术遣人送粮饷来了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.86,0:36:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}送来多少
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.16,0:37:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他给了我整整二十万
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.86,0:37:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二十万
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.76,0:37:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天哪 这太不像袁术所为了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.87,0:37:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太不像了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.37,0:37:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先 你想过没有
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.84,0:37:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他给你送来这么多粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.01,0:37:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底要你为他做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.05,0:37:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他想取小沛
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.85,0:37:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大军来袭时
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.25,0:37:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他让我不要帮刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.35,0:37:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}离间之计啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.32,0:37:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.32,0:37:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.52,0:37:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小沛一旦落入袁术之手
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.03,0:37:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么我们徐州城等于是唇亡齿寒
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.23,0:37:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下一步要收拾的可就是我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.74,0:37:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是我已经收了袁术的粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.74,0:37:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道还能退回去不成
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.24,0:37:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然要退回去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.94,0:37:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}否则的话
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.75,0:37:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就等于结下了两个敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.55,0:37:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术和刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.85,0:37:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二十万粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.65,0:38:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这可是两年的开销
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.82,0:38:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这 这怎么能不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.52,0:38:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道你想去助袁术取下小沛
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.63,0:38:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走自取灭亡之路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.84,0:38:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不助袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.84,0:38:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不助刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.44,0:38:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}开战之时
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.94,0:38:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我让他们两家罢兵言和
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.95,0:38:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.45,0:38:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪里会有这等的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.85,0:38:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们连天子的话都可以不听
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.95,0:38:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会听你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.36,0:38:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们可以试一试嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.22,0:38:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来先生坐下陪我喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.93,0:38:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉 给先生唱首曲子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.13,0:38:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.33,0:38:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}行了 行了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.63,0:38:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先啊 你就自得其乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.03,0:38:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还有些事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.15,0:39:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 来 继续再来 接着拔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.35,0:39:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来来来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.66,0:39:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}赢了的有赏
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.86,0:39:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是个心智单纯的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.33,0:39:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.03,0:39:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜见主公
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.33,0:39:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布已复我一封密信
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.74,0:39:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说发誓不助刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.24,0:39:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们现在可以放心地取小沛了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.85,0:39:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各位将军
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.25,0:39:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们谁敢领兵攻刘备啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.16,0:39:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}纪灵愿率军出征
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.86,0:39:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.23,0:39:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备刚刚受挫不久
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.33,0:39:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小沛守军不过两万
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.73,0:39:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我给你五万大军
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.03,0:39:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}限你十日之内 攻克刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.74,0:39:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.64,0:40:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听令
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.64,0:40:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我率大军作为后援
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.65,0:40:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布如果有所异动
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.65,0:40:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一并剿灭
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.75,0:40:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.46,0:40:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}子龙
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.76,0:40:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我把实情告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.63,0:40:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们名义上有两万精兵
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.93,0:40:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实际上一万都不到
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.84,0:40:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么少
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.54,0:40:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}翼德和云长已分兵据守
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.84,0:40:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我心里有数
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.14,0:40:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小沛城池浅陋
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.85,0:40:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们断难迎敌
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.25,0:40:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我们只能请吕布发兵相援了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.96,0:40:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长和翼德都恨透了吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.96,0:40:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只好你去致一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.13,0:41:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这就去
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.43,0:41:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但如果
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.54,0:41:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布他不肯发兵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.94,0:41:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你就去拜见陈宫
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.34,0:41:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我并不是说陈宫比吕布更友善
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.34,0:41:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而是陈宫比吕布更聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.45,0:41:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他知道小沛一旦有失
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.75,0:41:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州早晚不保
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.35,0:41:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.65,0:41:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}领命
